---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Scale } from 'lucide-react';

---

<Layout title="Terms & Conditions - WH Pubs">
	<main class="pt-24 pb-32">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-4">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
				<div class="flex items-center justify-center mb-8">
					<div class="bg-secondary/10 p-4 rounded-full">
						<Scale class="w-12 h-12 text-primary" />
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<div class="prose max-w-none">
					<h1 class="text-center">Terms & Conditions</h1>
					<p class="text-lg text-center mb-12">Last updated: March 21, 2024</p>

					<h2>1. Introduction</h2>
					<p>These terms and conditions govern your use of WH Pubs' websites and services. By using our services, you accept these terms in full.</p>

					<h2>2. Booking Terms</h2>
					<h3>2.1 Reservations</h3>
					<p>All reservations are subject to availability. A valid credit/debit card may be required to secure certain bookings.</p>

					<h3>2.2 Cancellations</h3>
					<p>Please provide at least 24 hours' notice for cancellations. Late cancellations or no-shows may incur a charge.</p>

					<h2>3. Payment Terms</h2>
					<p>We accept all major credit and debit cards. Prices are inclusive of VAT where applicable.</p>

					<h2>4. Code of Conduct</h2>
					<p>We reserve the right to refuse service to anyone who:</p>
					<ul>
						<li>Displays inappropriate behavior</li>
						<li>Is under the influence of excessive alcohol</li>
						<li>Violates our establishment's policies</li>
						<li>Harasses staff or other customers</li>
					</ul>

					<h2>5. Gift Vouchers</h2>
					<p>Gift vouchers are:</p>
					<ul>
						<li>Valid for 12 months from date of purchase</li>
						<li>Non-refundable and non-transferable</li>
						<li>To be used in a single transaction</li>
					</ul>

					<h2>6. Events & Private Hire</h2>
					<p>Special terms apply for events and private hire. Please contact individual establishments for details.</p>

					<h2>7. Liability</h2>
					<p>We take all reasonable precautions to ensure your safety but cannot accept liability for:</p>
					<ul>
						<li>Personal belongings left on premises</li>
						<li>Accidents due to customer negligence</li>
						<li>Circumstances beyond our reasonable control</li>
					</ul>

					<h2>8. Intellectual Property</h2>
					<p>All content on our websites and marketing materials is protected by copyright and other intellectual property rights.</p>

					<h2>9. Data Protection</h2>
					<p>We process personal data in accordance with our Privacy Policy and applicable data protection laws.</p>

					<h2>10. Changes to Terms</h2>
					<p>We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Changes will be posted on our website.</p>

					<h2>11. Contact Information</h2>
					<p>For questions about these terms, please contact us at:</p>
					<ul>
						<li>Email: legal@whpubs.co.uk</li>
						<li>Phone: 0800 123 4567</li>
						<li>Address: WH Pubs Head Office, Kent, UK</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>